snippet.title: Amber Heard Returns To LA With Beefy Bodyguard On Her Arm
snippet.description:
Wednesday, June 22, 2016 - Amber Heard returned to LA from London with a beefy bodyguard looking too close for comfort at LAX. Has she hired protection to ward off her allegedly abusive estranged husband Johnny Depp? The two were rumored to be settling their differences out of court after a restraining order hearing was canceled last week.
